I'd say several cliches would be the many commonalities found among players. A bunch are either edgy teenagers experimenting with political ideas, stacks upon stacks of introverts, some have really really close attachments to self-created fictional characters, others have Aspergers and other things throughout the spectrum, a bunch are strongly influenced by their online LGBT identity in creating content, many have mental issues, and according to one poll in NSG from a long time ago, the majority (claim to) have IQ substantially higher than the general population.

My headcanon is quite simple. People like this including me in some sectors especially in the past dominate NS, because if they don't have these, then they won't spend their time on NS. They'd (as of 2021, metaphorically) go outside instead
